name: SUPERADMIN
description: Automatically has access to all other permissions, as well as future perms.

name: MODERATOR
description: For Moderators

name: VIEW_PERMISSIONS_PAGE
description: Gives View Access to this page.

name: ADMIN
description: Can access most of the areas and permissions

name: VIEW_ROLES_PAGE
description: Gives View Access to the Roles Page.

name: VIEW_AUDIT_PAGE
description: Gives View Access to the audit page.

name: POST_ANNOUNCEMENT_DISCORD
description: Allows a user to post using a discord Webhook.

name: POST_ANNOUNCEMENT_TWITTER
description: Allows a user to post to twitter.

name: DELETE_DISCORD_SETTINGS
description: Allows a user to delete a discord settings instance

name: UPDATE_DISCORD_SETTINGS
description: Allows a user to update a Discord Setting instance.

name: CREATE_DISCORD_SETTINGS
description: Allows a user to create new Discord Settings Instances.

name: VIEW_DISCORD_SETTINGS
description: Allows a user to View the Discord Settings Page.

name: EDIT_TWITCH_SETTINGS
description: Allows a user to update Twitch Settings.

name: DELETE_TWITCH_SETTINGS
description: Allows a user to delete Twitch Settings.

name: CREATE_TWITCH_SETTINGS
description: Allows a user to create Twitch Settings.

name: VIEW_TWITCH_SETTINGS
description: Allows a user to view Twitch Settings.

name: VIEW_ROLES
description: Allows a user to view roles assigned to others.

name: CREATE_ROLE
description: Allows a user to create new roles. This includes assigning new Permissions. Be careful with this.

name: UPDATE_ROLE
description: Allows a user to update existing roles.

name: DELETE_ROLE
description: Allows a user to delete existing roles.

name: VIEW_USER
description: Allows a user to view other users.

name: VIEW_USERS_PAGE
description: Allows a user to see the user page.
